// throws so callers fail loudly during boot — the Firebase init in `main.dart`
// is gated behind `kEnableFirebaseAuth`, so this only fires after the flip.
//
// Generation steps for the user (one-time):
//   1. In Firebase console, register iOS bundle `com.togodynamics.nootoV2` and
//      Android package `com.togodynamics.nootoV2` under project `nooto-dev`.
//   2. From `app-v2/`, run: `flutterfire configure --project=nooto-dev`.
//   3. Confirm the wizard writes `lib/firebase_options.dart`,
//      `ios/Runner/GoogleService-Info.plist`, and
//      `android/app/google-services.json`.
//   4. Flip `kEnableFirebaseAuth` to `true` in `lib/env_flags.dart`.

